Class Jobs

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.uws.Jobs
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
@Entity @VoDml(id="uws:jobs", role=objectType) public class Jobs extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
The list of job references returned at /(jobs) The list presented may be affected by the current security context and may be filtered. objectType: Jobs
